                    <lb n="1"/>cakāttam <num value="1538"><g type="numeral">1000</g> 5 <g type="numeral">100</g> 3 <g type="numeral">10</g> <unclear>8</unclear></num> ṉ cellāniṉṟa srī <unclear>perumāḷ</unclear> cīvala māṟaṉ varakuṇa<unclear>rā</unclear>maṉ-āṉa pāṇṭiya-kulacēkara-cōmāciyāṟku Āṇṭu mūṉṟ-āvatu naḷa
