                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>kkukār <unclear>paṇam</unclear> 6 pācāṉaM <unclear>paṇam</unclear> 6 Āka-p paṇaM ppaṉṉiraṇṭuM cuvāmikku neyviḷakkukku-k kaṭṭaḷaiyiṭṭōM Appaṭiyē
                    <lb n="5"/>Ācantirāṟkañ cantatippiṟavēcamē cuvāmiyuṭaiya kuṭiyāka-k kaṭṭaḷaiyiṭṭōm appaṭiyē kaiyyāṇṭu ko
